<!doctype html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<meta http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible' content='IE=edge;chrome=1' />

		<!-- Use title if it's in the page YAML frontmatter -->
		<title><%= data.page.title || "The Middleman" %></title>


		<link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Source+Sans+Pro:400,200,200italic,400italic,700' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>

		<%= stylesheet_link_tag "normalize", "all" %>
		<%= javascript_include_tag  "all" %>
	</head>
	<body>

		<div class="page">

			<header>
				<nav>
					<ul>
						<li><a href="/" id="logo">no<small>way</small></a></li>
					</ul>
				</nav>

				<aside>
					<ol>
						<% blog.tags.each do |tag, articles| %>
							<li><%= link_to tag, tag_path(tag) %></a></li>
						<% end %>
						<% blog.articles.group_by {|a| a.date.year }.each do |year, articles| %>
							<li><%= link_to year, blog_year_path(year) %></a></li>
						<% end %>
					</ol>
				</aside>
			</header>

			<section id="main" role="main">
				<%= yield %>
			</section>


			<aside>
			<% if paginate %>
				<ul class="paginate-menu">
						<% if prev_page %>
							<li id="goto_prev"><%= link_to 'Previous page', prev_page %></li>
						<% end %>
						<% if page_number != num_pages %>
							<li>Page: <%= page_number %> sur <%= num_pages %></li>
						<% end %>
						<% if next_page %>
							<li id="goto_next"><%= link_to 'Next page', next_page %></li>
						<% end %>
					</ul>
			<% end %>

		</aside>

			<footer>
			<div class="bloc">
					<h2>Articles récents</h2>
					<ol>
						<% blog.articles[0...5].each do |article| %>
							<li><%= link_to article.title, article %> <span><%= article.date.strftime('%d.%m.%y') %></span></li>
						<% end %>
					</ol>
				</div>

				<div class="bloc">
					<h2>Qui suis-je ?</h2>
					<p>Phasellus accumsan, nulla at laoreet molestie, lorem leo cursus velit, at ullamcorper mauris metus quis odio. Class aptent taciti sociosqu ad litora torquent per conubia nostra, per inceptos himenaeos. Donec vel tortor eros, tincidunt interdum ligula. Nullam sit amet ipsum nisi, commodo malesuada neque. <a href="#" title="Lire la page 'à propos'">Lire la suite</a></p>
				</div>
				<ul class="copyright">
						<li>© 2010-2013</li>
						<li><strong>No Way</strong></li>
						<li>Noëlie Amiot</li>
				</ul>
			</footer>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
